lead_paragraph: THE BARK COQUETTE.--EDWARD C. GENET, of this city, in a letter enclosing the correspondence published below, expresses the confident belief that the officers, passengers and crew of the missing bark Coquette, still survive, from the fact that the vessel is ascertained to have been wrecked on the island of Formosa;
